oai_dc:dc.dc:title: St. John's Episcopal Church interior
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: J.W. Stewart, Knoxville
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: St. John's Episcopal Church interior, Knoxville, TN. View in sanctuary looking towards altar. Ca. 1880? Taken by J.W. Stewart, Knoxville, TN. Note on back of photograph: Where Annie McGhee and Calvin McClung were married. Shows pews, pulpit, pipes of organ, altar.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Episcopal churches; Altars; Pulpits; Pews;
